          'Fast, efficient, and with great attention to detail. The final result exceeded our expectations and was delivered ahead of schedule.',
        name: 'E-commerce Founder',
        job: 'Online Store',
        image: {
          src: '~/assets/images/profile.jpg',
          alt: 'Avatar of E-commerce Founder',
        },
      },
      {
        testimonial:
          'The new user interface he designed is intuitive and has drastically improved our team\'s productivity. Highly recommended.',
        name: 'Product Lead',
        job: 'B2B SaaS',
        image: {
          src: '~/assets/images/profile2.jpg',
          alt: 'Avatar of Product Lead',
        },
      },
      {
